title: Flight Simulator 2020 - World Update V - Goteborg
description:
In this video we will look at the city of Goteborg. We are depart from Goteborg Landveter and fly over the city which has been updated as part of World Update V: Nordics which has been released today. After this we will continue to fly to the North an use the travel to functionality to pay a short visit to the Uddevalla Bridge.

0:00 title screen
0:10 departing from Goteborg Landveter
05:40 arriving at Goteborg city
18:40 arriving at Uddevalla Bridge
